back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 25, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cmg1665702615110.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cmg1665702615110.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cmg1665702615110.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cmg1665702615110\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls whether the Close caption button works only within the context of the form\n    component of which it is part.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__topic_d146402e1_d146403e1_d146404e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__p_d146405e1_d146406e1_d146407e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">CloseContext</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__section_n5x_5f4_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967489e67\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__ul_dym_vf4_yvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__li_d51038e1_d51039e1_d51040e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>—the Close caption button of an inactive form component, such as a\n          parent form of a modal form, is disabled and cannot be used to close either the parent\n          form or the child form. The active modal child form can be closed only by its own Close\n          caption button. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__li_d51041e1_d51042e1_d51043e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—pressing the Close caption button of any form causes the form that\n          has focus to be closed. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__table_d17900e1_d17901e1_d17902e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzj1665702614359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzj1665702614359.html\" title=\"The [upi] section of the initialization file determines the appearance or behavior of many Universal Presentation Interface (UPI) objects under Microsoft Windows.\">[upi]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cmg1665702615110__section_ejj_wf4_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967489e126\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">In tab pages, the form components that implement the tab pages do not have Close caption\n        buttons. Only the parent, the form component that contains the tab widget, has a Close\n        caption button. If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">CloseContext</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>, the Close\n        caption button always invokes a quit request on the parent form, irrespective of whether the\n        tab or the parent form has focus. If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">CloseContext</span> is set to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>, clicking the Close caption button invokes a quit request on the form\n        that has focus.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>utab (Tab)</a><p>The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "CloseContext Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 25, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controls whether the Close caption button works only within the context of the form component of which it is part. CloseContext = on | off Arguments on —the Close caption button of an inactive form component, such as a parent form of a modal form, is disabled and cannot be used to close either the parent form or the child form. The active modal child form can be closed only by its own Close caption button. off —pressing the Close caption button of any form causes the form that has focus to be closed. Default value on File section [upi] Description In tab pages, the form components that implement the tab pages do not have Close caption buttons. Only the parent, the form component that contains the tab widget, has a Close caption button. If CloseContext is set to on , the Close caption button always invokes a quit request on the parent form, irrespective of whether the tab or the parent form has focus. If CloseContext is set to off , clicking the Close caption button invokes a quit request on the form that has focus. Related Links utab (Tab) The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}